        "Id" : "event_co_closeEncounter",
        "Name" : "Close Encounter",
        "Details" : "You rush to the bridge upon receiving Sumire's hails. At first glance, you immediately notice everyone looking outside the Argo's port side windows.\r\n\r\nSumire responds without taking her eyes off the spectacle before her, \"You'll want to see this Commander?\"\r\n\r\nEven though it is a healthy distance away, you can make out the pair of ships in a fierce firefight. One is clearly a pirate vessel attacking a similarly sized cargoship. \r\n\r\n\"I never thought I'd live to see a Buccaneer holdin' its own, Commander.\" Yang grins, \"She's givin' as good as she's gettin'. I can barely make it out but I think she's sporting a pair of Gauss rifles!\"\r\n\r\nDr. Murad laments, \"Isn't someone going to do something? They're being attacked by pirates!\"\r\n\r\n\"I could scramble the Leopard?\", Sumire chimes in.\r\n\r\nDarius just turns to you with a shrug, \"Well, it's up to you Commander?\"",
