                    "Description" : {
                        "Id" : "outcome_0_0",
                        "Name" : "Mind your business",
                        "Details" : "Turning away from the firefight, you shake your head declining the temptation to get involved.\r\n\r\n\"No point sticking our necks out and putting our own people at risk...especially for free.\"\r\n\r\nMurad protests, \"You're just going to leave them to the mercy of those pirates?\"\r\n\r\nYou look at her dead in the eyes with a steely glance, \"How many people came to our rescue the countless times Pirates were harassing us? It's not our fight, but if it makes you feel any better, with dual Gauss Rifles they are better armed than us.\"\r\n\r\nThe staff nods as everyone quietly goes about their business as nothing ever happened.",
