            "ResultSets" : [
                {
                    "Description" : {
                        "Id" : "outcome_1_0",
                        "Name" : "Cavalry",
                        "Details" : "Scrambling the Leopard, Sumire deftly shoots several shots across the bow of the heavily damaged Pirate ship. The bandits decide to make a hasty retreat but not without snarling a series of empty threats as they flee. The captain of the equally battered Buccaneer hesitantly agrees to your offer of aid. Soon Sumire is ferrying a small group of MechTechs, including Yang, to assist with the repairs. Hours later, Sumire returns to the Argo with an overjoyed Yang storming out of the Leopard, arms outstretched, eagerly presenting the bountiful 'reward' on display. All compliments of one very thankful Buccaneer captain. \r\n\r\nYang excitedly blurts, \"Gus even said that if we ever cross paths again, he might have even better stuff at ridiculously low prices for his new favourite customers!\"\r\n\r\nDarius smiles, \"Ridiculously low prices? I like the sound of that!\"\r\n\r\nSumire disembarking chimes in, \"Commander, Gus insists that you hail him before we leave.\"\r\n\r\nYou promptly head back to the bridge to talk to your newfound benefactor.",
